            <description><![CDATA[<h2>1.5.1</h2>
<p>Slow 'reasoning' models are now labeled in Settings (they think for a long time before answering), Otto shows when a model is thinking instead of sitting silent, and Otto never auto-picks one.</p>
]]></description>
