        <item>
            <title>1.5.0</title>
            <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jul 2026 10:03:31 -0700</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>10</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.5.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>13.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description><![CDATA[<h2>1.5.0</h2>
<p>Otto is faster and has a whole new look. Replies now stream in word by word, and the local brain answers in a couple of seconds instead of twenty. The design is rebuilt in a calm near-black style with a warm amber accent — the same feel as the Martin assistant.</p>
]]></description>
